<section class="page-faq">
  <div class="page-faq__inner">

    <h1 class="page-faq__title">FAQ</h1>
    <p class="page-faq__subtitle">HYPER REAL LOVE IS A BRAND THAT INSPIRES YOU TO WORK ON YOUR SELF, TOGETHER.</p>

    <div class="page-faq__list">

      <details class="page-faq__item">
        <summary class="page-faq__question">Why work on my Self?</summary>
        <div class="page-faq__answer">
          <p>To create a continuous cycle of self-discovery and authentic action. Each step deepens your understanding and rids you of limiting beliefs. We believe that by working on your Self, you:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>love who you are today, not tomorrow</li>
            <li>learn to respond, not react</li>
            <li>realize your potential, not others'</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="page-faq__item">
        <summary class="page-faq__question">What steps can I take to work on my Self?</summary>
        <div class="page-faq__answer">
          <ol>
            <li>Dedicate intentional time</li>
            <li>Observe your patterns</li>
            <li>Question with brutal honesty</li>
            <li>Practice acceptance</li>
            <li>Transform your own reality, beyond your limitations</li>
            <li>Communicate authentically</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="page-faq__item">
        <summary class="page-faq__question">What does HYPER REAL LOVE stand for?</summary>
        <div class="page-faq__answer">
          <p>The meaning is unique to each person — that's why we chose it. For us, it's "to see what there isn't yet, from a place of love" — creating your own reality with care, rather than fear.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="page-faq__item">
        <summary class="page-faq__question">Who are you to guide me on this journey?</summary>
        <div class="page-faq__answer">
          <p>We're not here to prescribe your path. The work is yours to do. The discoveries yours to make. Because transformation isn't something we give you — it's something you uncover yourself, one authentic choice at a time. We're here to inspire you to start.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="page-faq__item">
        <summary class="page-faq__question">How does HYPER REAL LOVE inspire?</summary>
        <div class="page-faq__answer">
          <p>We inspire self-work with anchors, knowledge, exercises.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Anchors:</strong> Caps that question autopilot and spark conversation</li>
            <li><strong>Relatable knowledge:</strong> Stories and concepts that reveal how beliefs shape reality</li>
            <li><strong>Practical tools:</strong> Exercises that help you interrupt autopilot moments, learn, and act</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="page-faq__item">
        <summary class="page-faq__question">I still don't get it. What is all this? What are you offering?</summary>
        <div class="page-faq__answer">
          <p>You can call it a brand of change. We're offering caps and exercises to dedicate time to get to know your Self.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="page-faq__item">
        <summary class="page-faq__question">Why should I buy it?</summary>
        <div class="page-faq__answer">
          <p>To express your interest in deep connection with your Self and people around you.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="page-faq__item">
        <summary class="page-faq__question">What is your vision?</summary>
        <div class="page-faq__answer">
          <p>We see a world that is led by modern monks — individuals who practice daily personal awakening and act for change, rather than growth.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

